criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  it must be the first marriage for both the woman and her husband and they must
             currently live in the study area;

          -  the female's age must range from 20 to 34 years;

          -  the couple has no plan to leave the study area in which they live for the next two
             years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  those who are currently pregnant;

          -  those who have tried unsuccessfully to get pregnant for at least 1 year;

          -  those who are current or former smokers;

          -  those who plan to move in the coming year.
